ng of the minority class using SMOTE (Synthetic Minority Oversampling Technique), which resulted in the equal distribution of both the classes (0 and 1). Used the following modules in Python-Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-Learn, matplotlib, Imbalanced-learn Logistic Regression gave AUC=0.95, but the precision was very low (0.08). So, I tried Random Forests and it gave AUC=0.94 and precision=0.85 (with 'gini' criterion) and AUC=0.92 & precision=0.83 (with 'entropy' criterion). Measured performance metrics-accuracy, precision, recall, AUC and plotted ROC curve Used the following modules in Python-Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-Learn, matplotlib, Imbalanced-learn","topics":[],"score":2236,"base_score":2236,"python_score":2236,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"matthew-sessions/smart-label","owner":"matthew-sessions","html_url":"https://github.com/matthew-sessions/smart-label","stars":0,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":null,"topics":[],"score":2236,"base_score":2236,"python_score":2236,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"arnoldsmithson/sierpinksi_triangle","owner":"arnoldsmithson","html_url":"https://github.com/arnoldsmithson/sierpinksi_triangle","stars":0,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":"My code implementation in Python that'll draw a sierpinski triangle ","topics":[],"score":2236,"base_score":2236,"python_score":2236,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"younes778/CityU_AI510_PE02","owner":"younes778","html_url":"https://github.com/younes778/CityU_AI510_PE02","stars":0,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":"PE 02 for modeul AI510 @CityU DIT","topics":[],"score":2236,"base_score":2236,"python_score":2236,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"thedude42/adventofcode_2022","owner":"thedude42","html_url":"https://github.com/thedude42/adventofcode_2022","stars":0,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":null,"topics":[],"score":2236,"base_score":2236,"python_score":2236,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"madisonstehle/dungeon_adventure","owner":"madisonstehle","h